  announcementId: dolos_day2_morning_wakeup
  text: 'Rise and shine, Technician. Current time is 0600 hours.

    Prepare for
    another productive shift in service of the DOLOS Corporation, a subsidiary of
    the Erebus Holdings.

    Vital signs show a 4% increase in metabolic rate. All
    systems are functional.

    Please proceed to your Aegis Collar Supplement Dispenser
    for your mandatory daily wellness protocol at your earliest convenience.'
